Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要靠互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,構建未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧 路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪走這未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是天人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發動戰爭 扭曲世界的都是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫沙慈的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你准尉才會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自殺兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去路易斯也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打倒你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞．艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身為變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我們不是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了促成變革者的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而被人工製造出來的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原始變革體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把Veda還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲．阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若說原始變革體已經進化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已超越原始變革體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為凌駕真正變革者之上的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會再放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會虧待你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢利 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了實現永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你們就是其最大障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說要接受變革者的支配嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由更優秀的種族來統率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從理論上考慮也是正確選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他們是為引導人類而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要求任何回報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理想的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣會失去自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全的自由就是拋棄道德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其盡頭只有毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在有秩序的社會結構中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們將享受有限制的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在籠中接受保護反而舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂和平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣稱根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上擾亂世界的正是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在將世界交給變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能真正根除戰爭 為何不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有史以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們一直追求的理想鄉就要實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來不是由我們自身創造的就毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的錯誤必須由自己來抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則就沒有真正的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糾纏不清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼天人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GN Archer…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子殘量…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈．庫斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶她去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是超越變革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda不會交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 引導人類的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易…斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙…慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是純粹變革者的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希林 用TRANS-AM攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了用自己的意志 創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去托勒密會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 還不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導彈剩餘不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的生命 會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不容許！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這GN粒子是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是戰鬥的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那光輝是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒…一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剎那戰鬥的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是生命的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變吧 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代替沒能改變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 為了創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要變革！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦…腦量子波紊亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連我們都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷傑尼．雷傑塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純粹變革者的腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和Twin Drive連動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提高純度的GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會擴張人們的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成完全進化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這噁心的感覺是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的人把哥哥他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是那傢伙的弟弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值得一殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別東張西望 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看著瑪麗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼不可思議的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音直接在腦中響起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 畢利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明知你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻利用了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了實現永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決心為此而戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直愛看你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是聲昔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯中尉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就算一直恨你 報仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校也一定不會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口 你這叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要將上校這親生父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也背叛了軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的報應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他擾亂了永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校不是會做那種事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他對母親見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何 不試圖彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 那男人沒對我說一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是借口 還是謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒試圖理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親手殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要他理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為何不理解上校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校一定是為你著想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為何當時什麼也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說的話 誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機80%擊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 身體的疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 我…已經
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不用說了 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 這溫暖的光芒是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心彷彿要融化一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他心中的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照亮未來的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的座標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅哈羅 機體拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的GN粒子是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擾亂了我的腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我等到這一刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷傑尼．雷傑塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda拒絕與我聯線？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道系統被你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲 你休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧 提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S…Seravee 產生審判領域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與Veda連線的機體紛紛停止運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的支援被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞．艾迪這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪回了Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥即將結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於用上它了 提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 給我動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格說哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有這傢伙不能放過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原地不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙殺了父親、母親、艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾 我們真心相愛過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真心相愛過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 是你讓我相信人們能夠彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就算被世人唾棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被責難
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為天人的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是Veda的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞 艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會為你報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便給人蓋棺定論
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意識已經和Veda完全結合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作為變革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 作為原始變革體並不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有這種能力 才能拯救你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與Veda相連 使我得以知曉一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就為你們講述 伊奧利亞計劃的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 現在開始返航
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的武力介入行動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在矛盾中促成了世界的統合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算最終犧性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也必須實現人類意志的統一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的是防止人類懷揣著紛爭的火種進入外太空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類必須改變自身才能編織未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亦為與異類種對話做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee重創
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再仔細找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人能夠在審判領域中行動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越變革者的變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲．阿爾瑪克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘恩負義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能獲得這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全歸功於我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲．阿爾瑪克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成變革的二人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以未來為賭注 展開最後一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 再生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新時代的帷幕升起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們選擇的道路上充滿苦難與煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.83,0:24:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 他們仍舊奮勇直前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之煉金術師 4月5日下午5時開始播出
